    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with this absolute gem, and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor today! It has been pampered like one of the family\u2014not a scratch or a smudge in sight. It drives like a dream and still has that wonderful new-car feel. I'm looking for a great new home for it where it'll be just as appreciated. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
