    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered icon. The 3.2L inline-six remains factory-spec, featuring crisp individual throttle body response and a flawlessly functioning double-VANOS system. The chassis has undergone preventative subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral loads. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual to a variable M-differential lock. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the car retains its original VIN-matched panels and factory-spec suspension geometry. Meticulously maintained with a documented valve adjustment history, this is a turnkey investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
