      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level 2004 BMW M3, a true purist\u2019s specification featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This specimen boasts a factory-crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a perfectly calibrated variable M differential lock. The high-revving powerplant maintains optimal compression across all cylinders, with the double VANOS system recently overhauled for surgical precision. The chassis remains factory-stiff, benefitting from a preventative subframe reinforcement and a completely refreshed suspension geometry utilizing OEM bushings. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint depth is consistent with a climate-controlled lifetime. Zero evidence of track use or deferred maintenance; this is a turnkey investment for the discerning enthusiast seeking mechanical perfection.",
